"bulduğumuz ve tanıdığımız için çok mutlu olduk. Güvenle gidebilirsiniz."
msgstr ""
"She made a tooth from a tiny tooth with filling and it turned out "
"beautifully. Although I went to 3 doctors before and they all said it needed "
"to be extracted, Dr. Devrim took her time and put effort into making the "
"tooth. Thank you so much, doctor, we are very happy to have found and met "
"you. You can go with confidence."

#: clinic/templates/clinic/index.html:1492
msgid "Cem T."
msgstr "Cem T."

#: clinic/templates/clinic/index.html:1500
